        <item>
            <title>2.1.0</title>
            <pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 09:58:52 +0900</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy</link>
            <sparkle:version>42</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.1.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Features
- Multiple custom API providers: register DeepSeek, OpenRouter, GLM, Qwen, Kimi and more in Preferences → Providers
- Add from pre-built templates with one click — model mappings auto-filled
- Select provider per session from a picker in the Launcher
- Non-Anthropic providers automatically hide unsupported options (Effort slider, Auto permission)

### Changes
- Moved custom API configuration from Launcher to Preferences for cleaner session setup
- Legacy single-provider settings automatically migrate to the new multi-provider system
]]></description>
